title: Maintenance "over by 0:600"
body: Really wanted to bank some games inb4 Work. Damnit rito.

replies.body: Sorry, friend.  We try to give as much heads up as possible through our [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page.  Be sure to bookmark it for updates as we patch of have scheduled maintenance.  Everything should be good now!
